# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/platform/redirects/

# Redirect old color URL structure to new one
/color/:hex  /colors/:hex  301

# Ensure trailing slashes
/colors/*  /colors/:splat/  301!
/blog/*  /blog/:splat/  301!
/categories/*  /categories/:splat/  301!

# Redirect www to non-www (if needed)
https://www.hexcolormeans.com/*  https://hexcolormeans.com/:splat  301

# SPA fallback for client-side routing (if needed)
# /*  /index.html  200